    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "NORTHWEST\nOrient\nAIRLINES\n½ FARE\nFOR YOUR FAMILY\nMONDAYS\nTUESDAYS\nWEDNESDAYS\nMAY 6, 1949",
      "ALASKA\nNORTHWEST AIRLINES\nTO\nHAWAI\nTHE ORIENT\nCANADA\nTACOMA\n• SEATTLE •\n00 PORTLAND\nWENATCHEE\nDETROIT\nCHICAGO\nI NEAPOLIS\nUNITED STATES\nCLEVELAND\nPITTSBURGH\nWASHINGTON\nHONOLULU\nSEATTLE-TACOMA PORTLAND\n••... HONOLULU\nWESTBOUND\nEASTBOUND\nOne Way\n$160\nRound Trip\n$288\n( PLUS TAX)\n701\nTU. TH. SA.\nSeattle\n(PST) Lv. 11:00 p.m.\nPortland\n. Ar. 12:00 a.m.\nPortland\nLv. 12:45 a.m.\nHonolulu ....(HST) Ar. 12:05 p.m.\nWED. FRI. SUN.\nHonolulu.\nPortland\nPortland\nSeattle.\n702\nWE. FR. SU.\n. (HST) Lv.\n9:30 p.m.\n. (PST) Ar. 12:15 p.m.\n. Lv. 12:30 p.m.\nAr.\n1:30 p.m."
